{"word":"G1627 - ἐκφέρω - ekphérō - ek-fer'-o - Bear","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκφέρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekphérō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-fer'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bear</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொண்டு வா, வெளியே எடுத்துக்கொண்டு வா"},{"paragraph":"1. to carry out, to bear forth"},{"paragraph":"2. to (bring) lead out"},{"paragraph":"3. to bring forth, produce"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G5342 - φέρω - phérō - fer'-o/5342\">G5342</a>; to <i>bear out</i> (literally or figuratively): - bear, bring forth, carry forth (out).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}